query:
SELECT 
  CASE WHEN isTest = 1 THEN 'test' ELSE 'production' END as type,
  status, 
  COUNT(*) as count 
FROM webhook_logs 
WHERE createdAt > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR)
GROUP BY isTest, status
ORDER BY isTest, status
